# e2e-evidence/.gitignore
# Fine-grained exclusion patterns for validation evidence files
# Preserves inventory and report files for auditing

# Screenshots and images
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.webp
*.bmp
*.tiff
*.svg

# Video recordings
*.mp4
*.mov
*.avi
*.mkv
*.webm

# JSON evidence payloads (API responses, snapshots)
*.json

# Log files
*.log
*.txt

# HAR (HTTP Archive) files
*.har

# Binary/compressed artifacts
*.zip
*.tar
*.gz

# Preserve report and inventory files
!report.md
!**/evidence-inventory.txt
